e on the megascreens. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290980/extras/5eee4e95a133d515fb14ceda859d2824.poster.avif?t=1755251743\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290980/extras/5eee4e95a133d515fb14ceda859d2824.webm?t=1755251743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290980/extras/5eee4e95a133d515fb14ceda859d2824.mp4?t=1755251743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Keep yourself busy with activities</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The Arcade is brimming with things to do, with new minigames around every corner of the city. No time will be wasted because even something as simple as playing dice with a cat can boost a useful stat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290980/extras/f3ad3c7b03d63f7ae41aff6b23cfa9c5.poster.avif?t=1755251743\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290980/extras/f3ad3c7b03d63f7ae41aff6b23cfa9c5.webm?t=1755251743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290980/extras/f3ad3c7b03d63f7ae41aff6b23cfa9c5.mp4?t=1755251743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Find. Your. Parents.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">It won’t be easy in a world where everyone looks the same and real names are erased by decree. Mika must uncover leads and seek allies in a place where trust seems like a distant illusion. To reunite with her family, she’ll need to confront her deepest fears and doubts, pushing through a web of deception and uncertainty.</p>",
